Class Profiler.Section

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.spongepowered.asm.util.perf.Profiler.Section
  • Enclosing class:
    Profiler

    public class Profiler.Section
extends java.lang.Object
    Profiler section. Normal sections do nothing so that the profiler itself consumes minimal resources when disabled.
